name: Rhizome x TRLab: Journey through SEED

metadata.name: Rhizome x TRLab: Journey through SEED 1
metadata.description:
Rhizome x TRLab invites you to embark on a journey through SEED, exploring Rhizome's role in preserving generative artworks, and collecting unique artworks along the way.

To keep you on the right path, this NFT image will continuously evolve throughout the experience, reminding you when artworks become available to collect. As we transition from Summer (Part One) to Fall (Part Two), keep an eye out for each upcoming milestone.

Please note: This NFT is not an official artwork. 
For more information, visit: https://trlab.com/editorial/Introducing-Seed
